HEADER (fixed, 24 bytes):
  [0:4]   magic number: b'VKTR'
  [4:8]   format version: uint32 = 1
  [8:16]  dimension: uint64
  [16:24] slot_count: uint64

RECORDS (fixed-width, repeating):
  [0:8]          slot_id: uint64
  [8:8+dim*4]    vector: float32 × dimension

stride = 8 + dimension × 4 bytes per record
record N starts at: 24 + N × stride